Recap of all the tricks that Soju 🐰 learned in 2022 🥳

People often think only 🐶 and 🐱can learn tricks but with enough patience, 🐰 can learn tricks too 💪

1. KISSES: Groom/Kiss hooman on demand 
2. BELLY: Jump on hooman’s belly 
3. SHOPPING: Paws on shopping cart 
4. HAND: Give paw to hooman 
5. CUDDLES: Hop in between hooman’s 
6. SOFA: Wait until given ok to jump on sofa 
7. STICKS: Pick up sticks and put in bowl
